- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper describes a framework for building an unsupervised ST system using machine learning techniques. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper involves developing an AI system for speech-to-text translation. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may involve analyzing social interactions through speech-to-text translation.
